text: Victor Popa (15 April 1949 – 15 November 2020) was a Moldovan politician. He was a member of the Parliament of Moldova from 2010 until 2013. He left office when he was named a Justice of the Constitutional Court of the Republic of Moldova.Popa Victor Popa died on 15 November 2020 at the age of 71.A decedat Victor Popa, fost judecător la Curtea Constituțională ==References== ==Other websites== * Popa Victor * Site-ul Partidului Liberal * Canal multimedia PL pe YouTube * Parlamentul Virtual Category:1949 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Moldovan politicians Category:Judges
